{"tid":1327651,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"正式向新鴻基提出具體要求","createTime":"2019-07-17T16:19:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T16:45:55.000Z","uid":122994,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd55d7ee8a1ad8e03ae0375c2330299b09da463a","tid":1327651,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"各位手足，我地依家日日搞鳩新鴻基，佢地已經驚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n依家班友想spin去咩地契，想證明黑警係商場圍捕既正當性。<br />\n<br />\n合法？so what？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時d商場整到塊地濕左跣親人都要道歉要賠啦，咁抹地合唔合法呀，好合法；跣親人又洗唔洗還同道歉呀，緊係要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同一道理，新鴻基係714搞到咁多人受驚同受傷，好多人都依家都仲有陰影，咁就緊係要還佢老味啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地要提出具體要求，令向新鴻基既申訴行動可以聚焦同延續，包括：<br />\n<br />\n1. 就714血洗新城市事件向所以商場使用者及商戶致最嚴肅道歉<br />\n<br />\n2. 正式譴責警方非法襲擊商場使用者及令商戶有嚴重損失<br />\n<br />\n3. 承諾日後旗下所有商場會確保商戶及使用者兔受同類驚慌及受傷<br />\n<br />\n4. 向公眾公開所有714流血事件之前同警方交流既內容<br />\n<br />\n以上四點係基本，手足仲有無補充或者威力加強版，請留言提出，整合後交比文宣手足做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1b8fdf48f38889f634a11bb4d97e904ba25adaa","tid":1327651,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:20:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c650c106ab6617f2a72540eacb16d6f85cf83441","tid":1327651,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T16:21:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfd511d9cf6b71152a2a64d5f26f54b91dc80d8"